## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| `Error: Python module 'nevergrad' not found` | Run `reticulate::py_install("nevergrad", pip=TRUE)` |
| `prophet` install fails | Install `cmdstanr` first: `install.packages("cmdstanr")` |
| Optimization runs but produces no outputs | Check `iterations` and `trials` in `robyn_mmm()` call |
| Plots don't appear in RStudio | Set `plot_folder` to a writable path in `robyn_mmm()` |
| `reticulate` can't find Python | Set `reticulate::use_python("/usr/bin/python3")` before loading Robyn |

